snippet.title: Quantic Pinball - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
This is from the same studio that put out Zombie Pinball, but this one is actually pretty good and visually pleasing.

Quantic Pinball (C) Shine Research
Published by Plug In Digital
Also available on Xbox One, Android, iOS and OUYA
